The '''2016 Pine Bowl''' is a [[college football]] [[bowl game]] that will be played on Saturday, November 5, 2016 at the [[Sapporo Dome]] in [[Sapporo]], [[Japan]]. The 29th annual [[Pine Bowl (North Japan Championship)|Pine Bowl]] will have [[Hokkaido University]] representing the [[Hokkaido American Football Association]] playing host to a team from the [[Tohoku Collegiate American Football Association]]. ==References== {{Reflist}}
