'''Campeonato Paulista Série B2''' was the sixth level of the [[São Paulo (state)|São Paulo]] state professional [[association football|football]] championship, one of the [[Brazilian Football State Championship|Brazilian state championship]]s.
== List of champions == * 2001 - [[Sport Club Corinthians Paulista B|Corinthians B]] (''[[São Paulo]]'') * 2002 - [[Jabaquara Atlético Clube|Jabaquara]] (''[[Santos, São Paulo|Santos]]'') * 2003 - [[Força Esporte Clube|Força]] (''[[Caieiras]]'')
