{{Unreferenced stub|auto=yes|date=December 2009}}
'''Stade Municipal de Koulikoro''' is located in [[Koulikoro]], [[Mali]]. It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] and serves as the home stadium of [[AS Nianan]].  The stadium has a capacity of 8,000 people.

